long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
ReJez is an extension that plays Animal Crossing Fan Made music on the hour, all day, every day.

Features the talented Youtuber Jez!

ReJez is a fork from Nook, an extension that plays original Animal Crossing soudtracks

Not affiliated with Nintendo
